title: The Crabb Family Discography 1996-2007 (22 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
THE CRABB FAMILY DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 22 releases...

 * 1996 - Alive And Kickin'
 * 1996 - Still Holdin' On
 * 1997 - Yesterday, Today And Forever
 * 1998 - Prayer In Motion
 * 1999 - Best Of The Crabb Family
 * 1999 - Crabb Grass
 * 2000 - Live From Kentucky
 * 2000 - Pray
 * 2001 - A Crabb Collection - Fifth Year Anniversary Edition
 * 2001 - Living Out The Dream
 * 2003 - A Crabb Collection
 * 2003 - CrabbFest Live 2003
 * 2003 - The Walk
 * 2004 - CrabbFest Live 2004
 * 2004 - Driven
 * 2005 - Live At Brooklyn Tabernacle
 * 2005 - Super Southern Gospel
 * 2005 - The Locket
 * 2006 - Blur The Lines
 * 2007 - Letting Go
 * 2009 - Grand Finale - The Ultimate Concert Experience
 * 2012 - Together Again

The Crabb Family is a southern gospel group.  They have had sixteen No. 1 songs on the national radio charts.

In Christ,
TorrentTracts - September 2013
